{"tid":302302,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"真心推介動畫電影--千年女優","createTime":"2017-06-29T09:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T03:58:09.000Z","uid":8307,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36f1e3fd98563cb82596bf7f96ec8537fa3a2bc3","tid":302302,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">女優=女演員,唔係鹽濕野</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/e/ee/Sennenyoyu.jpg/220px-Sennenyoyu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fee%2FSennenyoyu.jpg%2F220px-Sennenyoyu.jpg&h=b1004b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千年女優講述一個已隱退既出名女演員-千代子用成世人時間交還一條鑰匙比人既故仔,故事情節都幾感人<br />\n<img src=\"https://spotlightonfilm.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/tumblr_mm3o47uysr1r5gkxho2_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspotlightonfilm.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F05%2Ftumblr_mm3o47uysr1r5gkxho2_500.gif&h=2aad41dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事中以一位為拍攝記錄片導演去訪問千代子,千代子講述佢既一生經歷作為開始<br />\n<br />\n畫面係現實同戲劇之間互相交錯,攝影師同導演容入係回憶畫面中,一個個回憶最後又連接埋一齊,呢種表達方式都幾特別,就算係睇畫面都非常值得一睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://38.media.tumblr.com/fb69f7355cf71cd8e427fbf05ce81792/tumblr_mkgwk03FMg1qzqnxxo1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F38.media.tumblr.com%2Ffb69f7355cf71cd8e427fbf05ce81792%2Ftumblr_mkgwk03FMg1qzqnxxo1_500.gif&h=6a857672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貼返段精華片段先:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nHzlOrEYDHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnHzlOrEYDHY&d=IFkiwC60%2BeML7qvL1%2FddyEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d90bffc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nHzlOrEYDHY</a><br />\n<br />\n因為女主角係演員,所以回憶中都會穿插左唔同類型既戲劇,NHK大河劇情節甚至係科幻電影情節都會有<br />\n<br />\n有啲似睇緊the man from earth套科幻片既感覺,相信如果鍾意呢套戲既人都應該會鍾意千年女優/今敏既作品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>線上睇link</strong>:<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av29209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav29209%2F&d=IFkiwC60%2BeML7qvL1%2FddyEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=f777eead\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av29209/</a>"},{"pid":"549ef05e920ab55e265e87ccd5318f25f5879e4a","tid":302302,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"有伏死全家!!!"},{"pid":"dcfd2662efb3026cf9db3c0a8c2fa34192701175","tid":302302,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"唔好推人做已故人士FANS OKAY?<br />\n<br />\n等一世都會咁孤寂"},{"pid":"1ecec421abf717a44280057a706da1a059624d4e","tid":302302,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好推人做已故人士FANS OKAY?<br />\n<br />\n等一世都會咁孤寂</blockquote><br />\n睇完呢套戲既最後你就會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8058c6d274d03d3ad4ccebe0db21da0c82a4ce7a","tid":302302,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好推人做已故人士FANS OKAY?<br />\n<br />\n等一世都會咁孤寂</blockquote><br />\n睇完呢套戲既最後你就會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOK 返屋企睇"},{"pid":"847af1bf3d5731d1ffe74ee66acffa5385a059c0","tid":302302,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8183555610e71ec18d90c1ed3b87f9b24278ed","tid":302302,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab3aee7e13c5b507315831a5ea587fa7e931f84","tid":302302,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017